{"id": "280299e93c739488620fd488dcb846d1fb8c46d8528994890d1ae8febc037589", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:0", "text": "We can assign different surface and displacement to different faces."}
{"id": "41f8b8d9305832af4bfca5adebc724fb5214af7a2291012c0303d32879a6391f", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:1", "text": "Setting Up Group"}
{"id": "1083a96b2a81ae45a7640b1f00edba371b01391c5126477494e78a4a903c054c", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:2", "text": "To add a selection of faces to a group:"}
{"id": "11e974f45b3860a1691e94056b0a7ebd05e7ae6bdf29111c958434efc82c8bac", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:3", "text": "Change your selection mode to primitives."}
{"id": "81bb92d4110ab8b0027ee774ad8a8965df912c6c1e5bd5a7896deb8c83e5ca7b", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:4", "text": "Select the faces in the Viewport."}
{"id": "ea0fa7c99163f4ebba0222663ee9fc7fe05b33c9d5fd1ebbd0abfdd1ea677e8c", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:5", "text": "In the Viewport"}
{"id": "d6ebbfa0bd02d5e7470a2b2e8d047435b469977e9e7a839144ab6455ba98a133", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:6", "text": ", hit the TAB key and select"}
{"id": "34ca0e76608842ff3e7d924a455a396a82f471052c15e3f2ed7f090ac702e5c1", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:7", "text": "Group"}
{"id": "5c89ced8dd0b9ff6c88c1419068fba736bc800b67dfb5c609d15e8c7aee1c1c2", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:8", "text": "to add the faces to the group."}
{"id": "5932e392c2e1cd16bdf33ab0ab543fa72940ef0881533391d62c0a28287ce81d", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:9", "text": "Assigning Material To Groups"}
{"id": "394ad457e01d9636e3fbc61306dc68b117fa18d3bf7d8dea99dd136cd04b6466", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:10", "text": "Add a"}
{"id": "616cb218a65b982f61fd738e24ebe00d5a2ae039c0d386fed975a51d51b772f8", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:11", "text": "Material"}
{"id": "837c8a3d62bc6a0a02b12b86257f1b5c401e17e9a9008df115b93d2d7cad718e", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:13", "text": "If you want to assign both Bxdf and displacement shader, you will need to connect to the collect_output both the surface and displacement shaders inside a PxrMaterialBuilder node."}
{"id": "6a99a8513303229401c510c76fd8104ef8c54aad4cd3366d7abd23a769edc88e", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:14", "text": "Assign your group to the material by setting the Material to either a collect vop (see above) or a Bxdf."}
